  "texts": [
    "This dataset consists of tweets carrying at least one of the 10 depression symptoms.",
    "We use this training dataset to create our first DSD model, called DSD-Clinician-1.",
    "To do so, we follow the steps stated below.",
    "We first remove all the tweets with labels \"Gibberish,\" \"Evidence of Depression\" (ED) and \"No Evidence of Depression\" (NoED) from a subset of DSD-Clinician-Tweets after applying MVCP.",
    "We call this dataset DSD-Clinician-Tweets-Original."
  ],
